what is CSS?

- Cascading style sheet. provide to make a simple attrective and animatated website.

how many ways to create CSS? / apply css?
(1) inline - using with style attribute.

(2) internal - using with style tag.

(3) external - make an external file using
.css extension and apply on html file with <link> tag.

syntax of CSS : selector { property : value;}

selectors :
there is element to select any particular area.

how many types of selector:
(1) element selector :
for ex, p { color : white; }

(2) class selector :
for ex, .div1 { color : white; }

(3) ID selector :
for ex, #div1 { color : white; }

(4) universal selector :
for ex, \* { color : white; }

(5) group selector :
for ex, h1,h2,h3 { color : white; }2